title: Time Deposits, Reporting Member Banks, Federal Reserve System for United States
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Four Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1919-1934 (2)--Original Data, 1934-1947 (3)--Original Data, 1946-1953 (4)--Original Data, 1952-1956. Data Are Computed By NBER From Weekly Figures Averaged For The Month. Data Are For 101 Cities. Source: Federal Reserve Board, Annual Report, 1930, P. 99; 1933, Pp. 185, 189, 191; Data For 1934: Federal Reserve Bulletin.

This NBER data series m14079a appears on the NBER website in Chapter 14 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter14.html.
